item.title: Eclipse Errors
item.dc:creator: @sageofmali sageofmali
item.description:
@sageofmali wrote:

frozon566:

looks like you didnt import the jars properly, when you imported the server into eclipse did all of the folders light up with errors and at the bottom does it say theres like 1000s of errors? if so you didnt import the jars with the server.

Yes, I did get that.[quote=“imsuperman05, post:3, topic:421393”]Right click ‘src’ then go to Build Path and click ‘Configure Build Path…’

It should open a screen with the build paths, and just remove the second “src,” and “src/server/model/players”[/quote]
I did that, still errors. I got my server to work, but I still have the 100 errors.

Read full topic
